[The risk is real and the warning prudent. Nonetheless, so far, no measles cases have been traced to those attending the World Football Championships in South Africa in 2011 or the European Football Championship in Poland/Ukraine in 2012, events which attracted spectators from all over the world and were preceded by similar travel alerts. It must be presumed that these alerts have achieved their propose and the travelling public bass responded positively - Mod.CP]


