[Neither of the above two press reports (from a common source) state that the suspected case in Winnebago County has been confirmed by laboratory analysis. Confirmation and information regarding the source of the infection are awaited.

Winnebago County is located in northern Illinois bordering Wisconsin. The population according to the 2010 census is nearly 300 000. The interactive HealthMap of the state of illinois can be found at: http://healthmap.org/r/2ovI. - Mod.CP]
